    "title": "Junior SEO Specialist at Craftsvilla",
    "description": "Grow your career with Craftsvilla! We are hiring a SEO Specialist for our Srinagar team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Craftsvilla:\nCraftsvilla is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Sc / M.Sc in Life Sciences\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Retention Marketing\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Flexible working hours\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Learning & development budget\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Srinagar, Jammu & Kashmir, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Craftsvilla!",
